        <line><delSpan spanTo="#c57-0037.01" rend="strikethrough"/>having overcome many difficulties
            succeeded</line>
        <line>at length in joining her lover in his retreat<anchor xml:id="c57-0037.01"/></line>
        <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
        <line>Such was the history of my beloved cotta</line>
        <line>gers. It <del rend="strikethrough">struck</del>
            <mod type="additions">
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear">impressed</add>
            </mod> me deeply, <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">&#x2013;</del>
                <del rend="strikethrough">and</del>
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough"><unclear reason="overwritten" extent="4" precision="low" unit="chars">prom</unclear></del>
                    <del rend="strikethrough">it fr</del></add>
            </mod> I learned <mod type="additions">
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear">from <del rend="scribble">it</del></add>
            </mod> to admire</line>
        <line>their virtues &amp; to deprecate the vices of mankind.</line>
        <line><mod>
                <add><ptr target="c57-0037.02"/></add>
                <del rend="strikethrough">But crimes were distant</del>
                <del rend="double-strike">But</del>
            </mod>
            <mod>
                <del rend="overwritten">a</del>
                <add place="intralinear">A</add>
            </mod>s yet I looked</line>
        <line>upon crime as a distant evil; <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">but</del>
                <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough">for</del></add>
            </mod> bene</line>
        <line>volence &amp; generosity were ever present</line>
        <line>before me &#x2014; <del rend="strikethrough">and</del> I <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">longed</del>
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough">ardently desired</del></add>
                <del rend="strikethrough">to make one</del>
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">inciting in me to desire to become an
                    actor</add>
            </mod> in the</line>
        <line>busy scene where so many admirable</line>
        <line>qualities were called forth and displayed.</line>
        <line><add><ptr target="c57-0037.03"/></add>But <del rend="triple-strike">I</del> in giving
                <del rend="strikethrough">the histor</del> an account</line>
        <line>of the progress of my intellect<del rend="double-strike">s</del>, I must not</line>
        <line>omit a circumstance <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">that took</del>
                <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">which occurred</add>
            </mod></line>
        <line><del rend="strikethrough">place</del> in the beginning of the month</line>
        <line>of August of <del rend="strikethrough">that</del>
            <add place="superlinear" hand="#pbs">the same</add> year.<milestone unit="paragraph"/></line>
        <line><add><ptr target="c57-0037.04"/></add>One night during my accustomed</line>
        <line>visit to the neighbouring wood where</line>
        <line>I collected my own food and brought</line>
        <line>home firing for <del rend="double-strike">p</del> my protectors, I found</line>
        <line>on the ground a leathern portmanteau</line>
        <line>containing several articles of dress &amp; some</line>
        <line>books. I <del rend="double-strike">se</del> eagerly seized the prize &amp;</line>
        <line>returned with it to my hovel. The books</line>
        <line>were fortunately written in the language</line>
        <line><add><ptr target="c57-0037.05"/></add> I had learned at the cottage; they
            consisted</line>
        <line>of "Paradise Lost" &#x2014; a volume of Plutarchs</line>
        <line>lives and the <mod>
                <del rend="overwritten">s</del>
                <add place="intralinear">S</add>
            </mod>orrows of Werter &#x2014; <delSpan spanTo="#c57-0037.06" rend="strikethrough"/>And
            these</line>
        <line>I<anchor xml:id="c57-0037.06"/>
            <mod>
                <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough">was</del></add>
                <del rend="strikethrough">delighted</del>
                <del rend="strikethrough">in</del>
                <add place="superlinear"><del rend="strikethrough">to</del> the</add>
            </mod> possess<mod>
                <del rend="overwritten">in</del>
                <add place="intralinear">ion</add>
                <del rend="strikethrough">g</del>
                <add place="superlinear">of</add>
            </mod> these treasures</line>
        <line><mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">which</del>
                <add><metamark>&#x2717;</metamark><ptr target="c57-0037.07"/></add>
            </mod> I could <del rend="strikethrough">now</del> continually study</line>
        <line>and <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">occupy</del>
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear">exercise</add>
            </mod> my mind upon <mod type="additions">
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear">the<mod>
                        <del rend="overwritten">m</del>
                        <add place="intralinear">se</add>
                    </mod> histories</add>
            </mod> when my</line>
        <line>friends were employed <unclear reason="smear" extent="8" unit="chars" precision="high">in their</unclear> ordinary</line>
        <line><mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">concerns</del>
                <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
                <add place="superlinear">occupations</add>
            </mod>. I can hardly describe to you the</line>
